---
// Strict one-page A4 resume - Chinese
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>方绪杰 · 一页简历</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/global.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/i18n.css" />
</head>
<body class="a4-page">

<div class="toolbar no-print">
  <div class="lang-switch">
    <a href="/zh/resume-onepage" data-lang="zh" class="active">中文</a>
    <span class="sep">|</span>
    <a href="/en/resume-onepage" data-lang="en">EN</a>
  </div>
  <a href="/zh/" class="btn">← 返回</a>
  <button class="btn primary" id="download-pdf">⬇ 下载 PDF</button>
</div>

<article class="sheet">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header class="top">
    <div class="top-main">
      <h1>方绪杰</h1>
      <p class="sub">南京林业大学 · 化学工程学院 · 林产化工专业 · 本科大二</p>
    </div>
    <div class="top-contact">
      <span>📧 2332797170@qq.com</span>
      <span>📱 133****4936</span>
      <span>🐙 github.com/XCmiaow</span>
      <span>📍 Nanjing, China</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- SUMMARY -->
  <p class="summary">林产化工专业本科生，GPA <strong>3.60</strong>，<strong>班级第 1</strong>、<strong>专业第 2</strong>。获国家励志奖学金、校三好学生。数学建模核心奖项：全国大学生数学建模竞赛<strong>江苏省一等奖</strong>，连续两年 MCM/ICM <strong>H 奖</strong>。具备 Python 建模、LaTeX 论文写作与 AI 工具链实践能力。</p>

  <!-- TWO-COL: Education + Target -->
  <div class="row-2">
    <section>
      <h2>教育背景</h2>
      <div class="item">
        <div class="item-head"><strong>南京林业大学 · 化学工程学院</strong><span>2024.09 - 至今</span></div>
        <p>林产化工专业 · 本科在读</p>
        <p>GPA：3.60 · 班级排名：第 1 · 专业排名：第 2</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>申请定位</h2>
      <p class="small"><strong>保研/评优</strong>：专业成绩、数学建模、综合荣誉与科研潜力。</p>
      <p class="small"><strong>求职/作品集</strong>：Python 建模、前端工程、AI 工具链与知识管理。</p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- HONORS - two column list -->
  <section>
    <h2>核心荣誉</h2>
    <div class="row-2 tight">
      <ul>
        <li>2025 / 2026 年 美国大学生数学建模竞赛 MCM/ICM H 奖</li>
        <li>2024-2025 学年 国家励志奖学金</li>
        <li>2024 年 全国大学生数学建模竞赛 江苏省一等奖</li>
      </ul>
      <ul>
        <li>第 22 届江苏省高等数学竞赛 本科一级 A 类三等奖</li>
        <li>MathorCup 高校数学建模挑战赛 区域赛二等奖</li>
        <li>校三好学生 · 大学生学科竞赛先进个人</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROJECTS -->
  <section>
    <h2>项目与竞赛实践</h2>
    <div class="item">
      <div class="item-head"><strong>数学建模竞赛实践</strong><span>Python · 论文写作 · 数据分析</span></div>
      <p class="small">围绕实际问题完成问题抽象、模型构建、数据处理、算法求解、结果分析与论文撰写。参与全国大学生数学建模竞赛、MCM/ICM 等赛事，并取得省级与国际级奖项。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <div class="item-head"><strong>个人学术简历网站</strong><span>Astro · HTML/CSS · GitHub Pages · CI/CD</span></div>
      <p class="small">基于 Astro 构建中英双语个人学术主页，包含组件化布局、暗色模式、语言自动切换、打印样式与 GitHub Actions 自动部署。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TWO-COL: Skills + Service -->
  <div class="row-2">
    <section>
      <h2>技能专长</h2>
      <p class="small"><strong>专业：</strong>有机化学机理、Clayden、March、有机合成切断法、林产化工基础</p>
      <p class="small"><strong>建模：</strong>数学建模、Python、LaTeX、Markdown、Origin</p>
      <p class="small"><strong>工具：</strong>HTML、CSS、JavaScript、React、Zotero、Obsidian、AutoCAD、Aspen Plus</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>学生工作</h2>
      <ul class="tiny">
        <li>班级学习委员（2024-2025），负责作业收发与学习事务协调</li>
        <li>教学信息员（2024-2025），负责教学信息传达与课程反馈收集</li>
        <li>白马校区第一届排球新生杯第一组织责任人</li>
        <li>参与"纸牌搭屋"志愿服务与红十字会无偿献血活动</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>

</article>

<script>
  document.getElementById('download-pdf')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    window.print();
  });
</script>

<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body.a4-page {
    font-family: "Noto Sans SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    background: #e8e8e8;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .toolbar {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px;
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .toolbar .lang-switch { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; font-size: 13px; }
  .toolbar .lang-switch a { color: #888; text-decoration: none; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .toolbar .lang-switch a.active { color: #1a1a1a; background: #e8e4d4; }
  .toolbar .lang-switch .sep { color: #ddd; margin: 0 2px; }

  .sheet {
    width: 210mm; min-height: 297mm;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 20mm;   /* ~56px each way — we'll handle content density here */
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  /* ── SCREEN typography ── */
  .sheet h1 { font-size: 26pt; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .sheet h2 { font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 800; color: #2f5168; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; border-bottom: 1.5pt solid #c9a227; padding-bottom: 2pt; margin-top: 10pt; margin-bottom: 5pt; }
  .sheet p, .sheet li { font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 1.35; color: #333; }
  .sheet .small { font-size: 9pt; }
  .sheet .tiny { font-size: 8.5pt; padding-left: 16px; }
  .sheet .tiny li { margin-bottom: 2pt; }

  .top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 8pt; }
  .top-main h1 { margin-bottom: 2pt; }
  .top-main .sub { font-size: 10pt; color: #555; }
  .top-contact { display: grid; gap: 1pt; font-size: 9pt; color: #555; text-align: right; white-space: nowrap; }

  .summary { font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 9pt; color: #333; }

  .row-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  .row-2.tight { gap: 8px; }
  .row-2 ul { padding-left: 14px; }
  .row-2 li { font-size: 9pt; margin-bottom: 2pt; }

  .item { margin-bottom: 6pt; }
  .item-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 1pt; }
  .item-head strong { font-size: 9.5pt; }
  .item-head span { font-size: 8.5pt; color: #888; }

  /* ── PRINT: enforced one-page A4 ── */
  @media print {
    @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }

    body.a4-page { background: #fff; padding: 0; }

    .toolbar { display: none !important; }

    .sheet {
      width: 210mm; min-height: auto; height: auto;
      padding: 17mm 17mm 15mm 17mm;
      box-shadow: none; border: none;
      page-break-after: avoid;
    }

    .sheet h1 { font-size: 20pt; }
    .sheet h2 { font-size: 9.5pt; margin-top: 7pt; margin-bottom: 3pt; padding-bottom: 1.5pt; }
    .sheet p, .sheet li { font-size: 8pt; line-height: 1.28; }
    .sheet .small { font-size: 7.8pt; }
    .sheet .tiny { font-size: 7.5pt; padding-left: 12px; }
    .sheet .tiny li { margin-bottom: 1pt; }

    .top { margin-bottom: 5pt; }
    .top-main h1 { font-size: 20pt; margin-bottom: 1pt; }
    .top-main .sub { font-size: 8.5pt; }
    .top-contact { font-size: 7.8pt; gap: 0; }

    .summary { font-size: 8pt; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 6pt; }

    .row-2 { gap: 10px; }
    .row-2.tight { gap: 6px; }
    .row-2 li { font-size: 7.8pt; margin-bottom: 1pt; }

    .item { margin-bottom: 4pt; }
    .item-head strong { font-size: 8pt; }
    .item-head span { font-size: 7.5pt; }

    * { page-break-inside: avoid; }
  }
</style>
</body>
</html>
